---

## Result

Epic 1 successfully established a clear understanding of the agricultural problem, stakeholder needs, business objectives, existing research, and the potential social and business impact of the OptiCrop system. This phase provides a strong foundation for the subsequent stages of data collection, preprocessing, machine learning model development, and application deployment.
